    3.811947824453816*^9, 3.8119478644680986`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "cde69b19-b5fe-465a-8020-d0094b7afe29"],
 ". We\[CloseCurlyQuote]ll come back to the Pauli exclusion principle and \
spin in a moment."
}], "Text",
