    3.811947824453816*^9, 3.8119478644680986`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "ef1b8221-9605-4ac3-b7b7-58ac88eb7fe5"],
 " should be the same for the helium atom, it seems we have a cyclic problem \
where we don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t know the value of  ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    SubsuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox[
      OverscriptBox[
       StyleBox["H",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"],
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "1", "eff"], "\[Phi]", 
