   3.844767312278656*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"45790f9d-cbe1-e044-ba6c-\
81bd14b543a4"],

Cell["\<\
where we have used the product rule of differentiation. Because each of the \
terms in the linear combination is independent,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811862762404212*^9, 
  3.811862862244412*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"98829394-d2a9-0440-9194-\
