    3.811862623167489*^9}, 3.8118626599418736`*^9, {3.8118627514300547`*^9, 
    3.8118627593819437`*^9}, {3.8118632270630903`*^9, 3.811863326828313*^9}, 
    3.8118634029600096`*^9, {3.8118635700628643`*^9, 3.811863574143609*^9}, {
    3.8118654741595607`*^9, 3.8118655915905437`*^9}, {3.8118658693746243`*^9, 
    3.811865896052101*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "faeebedd-74ed-784b-9c1c-d8afe38205f6"],
 ". Sometimes the process of finding the eigenvalues and eigenvectors is \
known as matrix diagonalization, so you might hear the process of finding the \
energies and wavefunctions referred to as \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]diagonalization\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8118659035007787`*^9, 3.8118659459237075`*^9}, {
