  ExpressionUUID->"6183dde9-130c-4af6-bb54-ed7e6ac763f3"],
 ". That means that in the end, we are typically solving a matrix equation, \
just as we did for the more generic linear variational method. We won\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]t go through the details, but this equation takes the form"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8127116985179663`*^9, 3.812711718666103*^9}, {
