7e8eb1c0c680"],

Cell["\<\
represents a correction for the anharmonicity of the potential. We can also \
write our wavefunction in the form of a perturbation to the known \
eigenfunctions of the unperturbed Hamiltonian,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119376040040426`*^9, 3.8119376130586343`*^9}, {
  3.8119376484973745`*^9, 3.811937684556222*^9}, {3.811937755676447*^9, 
