   3.811937882488633*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "8737a3b9-e191-8a4d-8843-a5f4e20a5058"],
 "is the energy obtained from the unperturbed Hamiltonian for a harmonic \
oscillator operating on the unperturbed harmonic oscillator energy \
