Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Second-Order Terms", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119401965614185`*^9, 
  3.811940198869959*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b9699949-0ae5-bd43-a86c-\
e20e467c3688"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "We also won\[CloseCurlyQuote]t go through the details of how the \
second-order terms are evaluated. Note that equation (158) doesn\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]t include all of the terms that are second-order in \
\[Lambda] (meaning they contain a ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["\[Lambda]", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9fd39a94-f929-3b42-8982-f38805895c47"],
 "). For that, we would need another term in our expansions. The second-order \
terms are in fact included and utilized in many types of computation."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119402122410645`*^9, 3.8119402268938184`*^9}, {
  3.8119407615212865`*^9, 3.811940762188183*^9}, {3.8119408700905275`*^9, 
  3.8119409298217144`*^9}, {3.8119519027397175`*^9, 3.8119519030736637`*^9}, {
  3.9362806863575497`*^9, 
  3.9362806870682793`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2ccf0011-dfdc-6f48-82c1-\
7a2601c12e5b"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Perturbation Theory and the Helium Atom", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811940976272234*^9, 3.811940983173987*^9}, {
  3.811941308960923*^9, 
  3.811941312979396*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"51081fc0-1f89-c14f-a465-\
8e6f2011a67f"],

Cell["\<\
Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s use perturbation theory to obtain an approximation of \
the ground-state energy of the helium atom. The starting point for our \
perturbation is similar to that for the variational method. We will again \
write the Hamiltonian in the form\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811940993597614*^9, 3.811941067225109*^9}, {
  3.8119411121154265`*^9, 3.8119411202559633`*^9}, {3.9362807155768013`*^9, 
  3.9362807222717724`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1ec12f8b-4640-d04f-9e45-\
41d158bbc166"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  OverscriptBox[
   StyleBox["H",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "H1"], "+", 
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "H2"], "+", 
   FractionBox[
    SuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox["e",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], 
    RowBox[{"4", 
     SubscriptBox["\[Pi]\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["r",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], 
      RowBox[{"1", ",", "2"}]]}]]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 
  3.8115994609014688`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dd8bb2a8-4e48-bf4b-8abb-\
b86db945e56e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "our unperturbed eigenfunction ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d3db8a50-9190-f04f-99c3-945425a5ec1d"],
 " will be the product of the wavefunctions of two hydrogen-like atoms,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119411358888483`*^9, 
  3.8119411662239895`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"046ac2d6-b4c9-5146-8089-\
de2ff0d54f65"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["r",
       FontWeight->"Bold",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"], ")"}], 
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["r",
       FontWeight->"Bold",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], ")"}]}], "=", 
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "1"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", "1"]}], ")"}], 
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "2"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", "2"]}], ")"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810112811439228*^9, 3.8101128248442793`*^9}, {
  3.810479494926491*^9, 3.8104795038498344`*^9}, {3.810479572543576*^9, 
  3.8104796147383184`*^9}, {3.8104802055659895`*^9, 3.8104802433915305`*^9}, {
  3.8104802785189395`*^9, 3.8104802814214115`*^9}, {3.8109915300785556`*^9, 
  3.8109916793993816`*^9}, {3.810991710031681*^9, 3.8109918292023373`*^9}, {
  3.810994488524798*^9, 3.810994499853472*^9}, {3.8109948928195066`*^9, 
  3.8109948950763626`*^9}, {3.8109949491606197`*^9, 3.810995087249513*^9}, {
  3.8109951188614283`*^9, 3.8109951226144466`*^9}, {3.8115998145208507`*^9, 
  3.8115999093225703`*^9}, {3.8119412228611946`*^9, 
  3.8119412966472034`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"be6218cd-2ed4-5c41-a5ff-\
fb8a5356d03e"],

Cell["\<\
Using this formulation of the unperturbed wavefunction, we see that we can \
write our Hamiltonian as\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119413373575845`*^9, 
  3.8119413724073076`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d72ae32c-69cc-b046-90ed-\
3d392112e4ca"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  OverscriptBox[
   StyleBox["H",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "+", 
   SuperscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 3.8115994609014688`*^9}, 
   3.8119413960962324`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"4d5872bc-6af4-f942-a2af-\
f161aa04ade4"],

Cell["where", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119413980204344`*^9, 
  3.8119413982717943`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4430acea-09c3-a24d-aac9-\
c7981c2f834a"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox[
   OverscriptBox[
    StyleBox["H",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["H",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "H1"], "+", 
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["H",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], "H2"]}], "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{"-", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}], 
      RowBox[{"2", 
       StyleBox[
        SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]], 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Del]", "1", "2"], 
      RowBox[{"-", 
       FractionBox[
        RowBox[{"2", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["e",
           FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]}], 
        RowBox[{"4", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Pi]\[Epsilon]", "0"]}]]}]}], 
     FractionBox["1", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"]]}], "+", 
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{"-", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}], 
      RowBox[{"2", 
       StyleBox[
        SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]], 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Del]", "2", "2"], 
      RowBox[{"-", 
       FractionBox[
        RowBox[{"2", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["e",
           FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]}], 
        RowBox[{"4", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Pi]\[Epsilon]", "0"]}]]}]}], 
     FractionBox["1", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]]}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 3.8115994609014688`*^9}, {
  3.8119413960962324`*^9, 
  3.8119414485702457`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f5436fe8-d038-004f-8c23-\
3bd411ee8208"],

Cell["and", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119414517014313`*^9, 
  3.811941451929431*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"12553f8b-18e7-9544-88b3-\
1e3719009d5e"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox[
   OverscriptBox[
    StyleBox["H",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]], "=", 
  FractionBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], 
   RowBox[{"4", 
    SubscriptBox["\[Pi]\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
    SubscriptBox[
     StyleBox["r",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     RowBox[{"1", ",", "2"}]]}]]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 3.8115994609014688`*^9}, 
   3.8119413960962324`*^9, {3.811941457027553*^9, 
   3.8119414629200516`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7d332652-fe0b-7e4f-8857-\
408430e65eb5"],

Cell["Note that", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119414657852616`*^9, 
  3.811941466539731*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"28b5d780-dbbd-394b-b4b9-\
e4d6a144e97f"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], 
   SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox[
    StyleBox["E",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], 
   SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 3.8115994609014688`*^9}, 
   3.8119413960962324`*^9, {3.811941483387253*^9, 
   3.811941501254716*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"299b0bc9-9dfe-8d46-8385-\
f56145f9cd5b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "That is, the unperturbed wavefunction ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.810112811439228*^9, 3.8101128248442793`*^9}, {
   3.810479494926491*^9, 3.8104795038498344`*^9}, {3.810479572543576*^9, 
   3.8104796147383184`*^9}, {3.8104802055659895`*^9, 
   3.8104802433915305`*^9}, {3.8104802785189395`*^9, 
   3.8104802814214115`*^9}, {3.8109915300785556`*^9, 
   3.8109916793993816`*^9}, {3.810991710031681*^9, 3.8109918292023373`*^9}, {
   3.810994488524798*^9, 3.810994499853472*^9}, {3.8109948928195066`*^9, 
   3.8109948950763626`*^9}, {3.8109949491606197`*^9, 3.810995087249513*^9}, {
   3.8109951188614283`*^9, 3.8109951226144466`*^9}, {3.8115998145208507`*^9, 
   3.8115999093225703`*^9}, {3.8119412228611946`*^9, 3.8119412966472034`*^9}},
  ExpressionUUID->"b4f28f86-494a-de44-bfd5-493cf761be63"],
 "is an eigenfunction of the Hamiltonian with energy eigenvalue ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.811599416354409*^9, 3.8115994609014688`*^9}, 
    3.8119413960962324`*^9, {3.811941483387253*^9, 3.811941501254716*^9}},
  ExpressionUUID->"607f63ab-0dd5-6248-9928-01be9e181718"],
 ". We already have a formula for the first-order correction to the energy, "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119415036285152`*^9, 
  3.8119415511888742`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"77dfbbb6-9409-cc42-a6f6-\
875966d7a634"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]], "=", 
  RowBox[{"\[Integral]", 
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}], "\[Star]"}]], 
    StyleBox[
     SuperscriptBox[
      OverscriptBox[
       StyleBox["H",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["1",
        FontSlant->"Plain"], ")"}]],
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    SuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], 
    RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"77dd5e0c-b96b-1d4f-a03f-\
dcc7a2441105"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"\t ", 
  RowBox[{"\[Integral]", " ", 
   RowBox[{"\[Integral]", 
    RowBox[{
     SubsuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
      RowBox[{"1", "s"}], "\[Star]"], 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"], ")"}], 
     SubsuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
      RowBox[{"1", "s"}], "\[Star]"], 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], ")"}], 
     FractionBox[
      SuperscriptBox[
       StyleBox["e",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], 
      RowBox[{"4", 
       SubscriptBox["\[Pi]\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
       SubscriptBox[
        StyleBox["r",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], 
        RowBox[{"1", ",", "2"}]]}]], 
     SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
      RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"], ")"}], 
     SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
      RowBox[{"1", "s"}]], 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], ")"}], 
     RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "1"]}], 
     RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", 
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["r",
        FontWeight->"Bold",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]}]}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.811941568859282*^9, 3.8119415723020415`*^9}, {
  3.8119416319232607`*^9, 
  3.8119416975514708`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c1b28cf1-8f7a-9044-a82e-\
c2cf2cf6ee99"],

Cell["We won\[CloseCurlyQuote]t go through evaluating this integral, but we \
obtain", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119417088172417`*^9, 
  3.811941720235538*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"96207e6b-2cea-a947-948e-\
ddf9733bc0ff"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   FractionBox[
    RowBox[{"5", 
     StyleBox["Z",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "8"], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{
      StyleBox[
       SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
       FontSlant->"Italic"], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       StyleBox["e",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
     RowBox[{"16", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
      SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
      SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], ")"}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 
  3.811941772989243*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a93b1b29-862e-e343-a23e-\
a708f80655cf"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "If we add this to ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
   3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
   3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 
   3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {
   3.8119396974949074`*^9, 3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 
   3.811941772989243*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "98cea658-803b-4b4d-ae38-7ef9d5a95014"],
 ","
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119417999400315`*^9, 
  3.811941812894901*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0bffc463-2118-3743-8cdb-\
e5d600167928"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"-", 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["Z",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], 
       SubscriptBox["m", "e"], 
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["e",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
      RowBox[{"32", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
       SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], ")"}]}], "-", 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox[
       StyleBox["Z",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], 
      SubscriptBox["m", "e"], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       StyleBox["e",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
     RowBox[{"32", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
      SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
      SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], ")"}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 3.811941772989243*^9}, {
  3.811941819461093*^9, 
  3.811941883219368*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ea16b415-67e7-0d45-b8fa-\
ed760a0491f5"],

Cell["we obtain", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119418933721237`*^9, 
  3.8119418988230457`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b7dd487-b26b-754c-9072-\
ac2667678e5d"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  StyleBox["E",
   FontSlant->"Italic"], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox["E",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "+", 
    SuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox["E",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]]}], "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"-", 
       FractionBox[
        SuperscriptBox[
         StyleBox["Z",
          FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], "2"]}], "-", 
      FractionBox[
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["Z",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], "2"], "+", 
      FractionBox[
       RowBox[{"5", 
        StyleBox["Z",
         FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "8"]}], ")"}], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{
       StyleBox[
        SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["e",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
      RowBox[{"16", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
       SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], 
     ")"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 3.811941772989243*^9}, {
  3.811941917141111*^9, 
  3.811941985367529*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c9ec8177-55ea-084b-a96f-\
9a5718abffd6"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"\t\t       ", 
  RowBox[{"=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"-", 
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["Z",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]}], "+", 
      FractionBox[
       RowBox[{"5", 
        StyleBox["Z",
         FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "8"]}], ")"}], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{
       StyleBox[
        SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["e",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
      RowBox[{"16", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
       SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], 
     ")"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
  3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
  3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {
  3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {3.8119396974949074`*^9, 
  3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 3.811941772989243*^9}, {
  3.811941917141111*^9, 
  3.8119419926630316`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e5da6bbf-3cc4-a844-80dc-\
4e17fbd30709"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For the helium atom, ",
 StyleBox["Z ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "= 2, so we obtain \[Minus]2.750 for our factor multiplying ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{"(", 
   FractionBox[
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox[
      SubscriptBox["m", "e"],
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     SuperscriptBox[
      StyleBox["e",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "4"]}], 
    RowBox[{"16", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], 
     SubscriptBox["\[Epsilon]", "0"], 
     SuperscriptBox["\[HBar]", "2"]}]], ")"}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.811939159903883*^9, 3.8119392103826303`*^9}, {
   3.8119393358094797`*^9, 3.8119393592738667`*^9}, {3.811939516691291*^9, 
   3.8119395296122313`*^9}, {3.8119395681458282`*^9, 
   3.8119395710471015`*^9}, {3.8119396323397303`*^9, 3.811939640127038*^9}, {
   3.8119396974949074`*^9, 3.8119397255363784`*^9}, {3.8119417277677493`*^9, 
   3.811941772989243*^9}, {3.811941917141111*^9, 3.8119419926630316`*^9}},
  ExpressionUUID->"34617c54-a2ad-2f46-ae52-cbce62a3776d"],
 ", whereas we obtained \[Minus]2.8477 using our effective nuclear charge \
method. The experimental result is \[Minus]2.9033. If we used second-order \
perturbation theory, we could obtain \[Minus]2.910, and higher-order \
perturbation would give us -2.9037. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811942002018448*^9, 3.81194212321859*^9}, {
  3.9362807478862762`*^9, 
  3.936280750919483*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5fb4f61a-256b-7d45-a608-\
f277600b1701"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Limitations of Perturbation Theory", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811942136390585*^9, 
  3.81194214291195*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7fc48d82-05ef-624f-90be-\
29a32565310e"],

Cell["\<\
We have seen that perturbation theory can be a highly effective method to \
obtain an approximation to the true energy and eigenstate of a system. \
However, its accuracy is limited both by the number of terms included and by \
the accuracy of the underlying \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]unperturbed\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] system. If we start with a case that does not even \
remotely resemble the true wavefunction, it is unlikely that we will be able \
to obtain an accurate answer through any reasonable number of perturbation \
terms.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8119421457145143`*^9, 
  3.8119422558844366`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"944fbc3e-deee-1f43-b257-\
e24a17bcf1b4"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
},
